      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid opportunity for someone who wants a budget-friendly driver, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It has honest wear consistent with age and use, and it\u2019s priced to reflect that. If you\u2019re after something inexpensive with room to make it your own, this could be a great fit.",
