      "description": "Strong-running used car with a dependable powertrain, smooth-shifting transmission, and solid road manners. Cosmetically it shows age and will benefit from TLC, but it remains a practical, affordable option for someone who wants reliable transportation or a straightforward project platform. Starts up, drives out, and offers good value for the money.",
